00:02.127 --> 00:04.254
Lois, are you about done

00:02.127 --> 00:04.254
in there?

00:02.127 --> 00:04.254
No!

00:04.296 --> 00:06.674
Well, you're gonna have

00:04.296 --> 00:06.674
to get out, I'm late for work.

00:06.715 --> 00:07.967
Hal, I am not cutting

00:06.715 --> 00:07.967
my shower short

00:08.008 --> 00:09.301
because you can't get

00:08.008 --> 00:09.301
out of bed in the morning!

00:09.343 --> 00:10.552
I can get up just fine

00:10.594 --> 00:13.054
if somebody didn't turn off

00:10.594 --> 00:13.054
my snooze alarm!

00:13.096 --> 00:15.056
That alarm went off

00:13.096 --> 00:15.056
every six minutes for an hour!

00:15.098 --> 00:16.266
What are you doing?

00:16.308 --> 00:17.058
I'm getting in, Lois.

00:17.100 --> 00:18.101
You are not!

00:18.143 --> 00:20.061
You will get your shower

00:18.143 --> 00:20.061
when I'm finished!

00:25.024 --> 00:27.653
I don't think I'll be able

00:25.024 --> 00:27.653
to come in today.

00:27.695 --> 00:29.947
I've got a pretty severe fever,

00:29.989 --> 00:33.074
scratchy throat, cough.

00:33.116 --> 00:35.076
(coughing)

